:: Start
Testing various Harlowe macros

(set: $name to "Alice")
(put: 100 into $health)
(move: $health into $maxHealth)

Basic macros:
(print: $name)
(display: "Fragment")

Conditional macros:
(if: $health > 50)[Healthy]
(unless: $health <= 0)[Alive]
(else-if: $health > 25)[Moderate]
(else:)[Critical]

Data structures:
(set: $items to (a: "sword", "shield", "potion"))
(set: $stats to (dm: "str", 10, "dex", 15))
(set: $uniqueItems to (ds: "key", "map"))

String operations:
(set: $greeting to (uppercase: "hello"))
(set: $count to (lowercase: "WORLD"))
(print: (str: $health))

Math operations:
(set: $result to (max: 5, 10, 3))
(set: $rounded to (round: 3.7))
(set: $absolute to (abs: -5))

Links:
(link: "Click me")[Revealed text]
(link-goto: "Next", "Chapter1")
(link-reveal: "Show more")[Hidden content]

Styling:
(text-colour: red)[Red text]
(bg: blue)[Blue background]
(font: "Arial")[Arial text]
(text-style: "bold", "italic")[Styled]

Transitions:
(transition: "dissolve")[Fading in]
(t8n: "slide-right")[Sliding]

Live macros:
(live: 1s)[
  Current health: $health
  (if: $health <= 0)[(stop:)]
]

Arrays and loops:
(for: each _item, ...$items)[
  Item: (print: _item)
]

Custom hooks:
|named>[This is a named hook]
(replace: ?named)[Replaced content]
(append: ?named)[Appended]

Game state:
(history:)
(visited: "Start")
(passage: "Start")

Saving:
(save-game: "slot1")
(load-game: "slot1")

Navigation:
(go-to: "Start")
(undo:)
(restart:)

Input:
(input: bind $userInput)
(dropdown: bind $choice, "Option 1", "Option 2")

